# Product Objects / Data Model

## 16. Main Entities

### 16.1 Prospects

Represents a person.

Fields:

* ID
* Name
* LinkedIn URL
* Email, if known
* Company
* Title/job
* Location
* Region
* Segment
* ICP type
* Company type
* Created at
* Updated at

### 16.2 Sender Accounts

Represents LinkedIn accounts used by Overtly team.

Fields:

* ID
* Account name
* Platform
* Owner
* Active/inactive
* Notes
* Created at
* Updated at

### 16.3 Message Templates

Represents outbound message versions.

Fields:

* ID
* Name
* Channel
* Template text
* Target segment
* Version
* Active/inactive
* Created at
* Updated at

### 16.4 Outreach Events

Represents a sent LinkedIn connection/message.

Fields:

* ID
* Prospect ID
* Sender account ID
* Message template ID
* Channel
* Message text
* Sent at
* Status
* Follow-up stage
* Notes
* Created at
* Updated at

### 16.5 Follow-Up Events

Represents each follow-up action.

Fields:

* ID
* Outreach event ID
* Prospect ID
* Sender account ID
* Follow-up number
* Follow-up message text
* Follow-up template/version
* Suggested by AI: yes/no
* Sent manually: yes/no
* Sent at
* Status
* Notes
* Created at
* Updated at

### 16.6 Replies

Represents logged replies.

Fields:

* ID
* Prospect ID
* Outreach event ID
* Reply text
* Reply date/time
* Reply type
* Sentiment
* Interest level
* Feature mentioned
* Objection mentioned
* Email mentioned
* Next action
* Created at
* Updated at

