# UX Requirements

## 17. Chrome Extension

The extension should include:

### 17.1 LinkedIn profile popup

Triggered when the user is on a LinkedIn profile and logs/sends an outreach action.

Fields:

* Prospect name
* Company
* Title
* Location
* LinkedIn URL
* Sender account
* Message version
* Message text
* Segment
* Notes
* Save button

### 17.2 Existing prospect detection

If a LinkedIn URL already exists in the database, the extension should show:

* Existing prospect found
* Current status
* Last message sent
* Follow-up stage
* Button: Log reply
* Button: Mark accepted
* Button: Mark follow-up sent
* Button: Open in dashboard

### 17.3 Follow-up helper

For a saved prospect, extension should show:

* Previous message
* Suggested follow-up
* Copy button
* Mark as sent button
* Log reply button

